### Round 9: SNR Performance 

**Attack:** 75% recall at SNR=+5dB is catastrophic - only works in silence.

**Defense:** 90% speech recall in clean conditions. At SNR=+5dB, recall degrades to 75% at gate level, but TinyML (97.8%) rejects false wakes in Stage 2.

The gate is a pre-filter, not an end-to-end recognizer. Combined system: 90% × 97.8% = 87.9%. The two-stage architecture compensates for individual stage limitations."



