### Round 10: Abort Rate Ceiling 

** 99.4% abort but Opt #6 shows only 52%. 
 The 99.4% abort was measured on synthetic LFSR noise only  that was premature validation. Real environmental noise (ESC-50) gives 52-70% abort.
However, power savings still hold at 92-93% across all conditions:
- Silence: 1845µW → 93% savings
- Noisy room (24 false wakes/s): 2162µW → 92% savings  
- During speech: 1973µW → 93% savings

The abort rate is lower than synthetic testing, but the gate still functions. I corrected this in Opt #6 documentation.
